Metadata.Title: Заказ на убийство: 1-18-2547050-20
Metadata.Description: Good afternoon 47, you have a very unusual assignment for today. A group of fanatics infiltrated a special medical facility in Hokkaido, their plan is to eliminate all staff. You have to destroy them before the right time, before they set up a stun gas bomb and killed all the staff. Get ready 47.
